---
import Indice from "../../components/Indice.astro";
import DashboardLayout from "../../layouts/DashboardLayout.astro";
---

<DashboardLayout background="bg-ambient">
  <Indice slot="sidebar" />

  <section class="hero h-full">
    <div class="hero-overlay bg-black/50" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="hero-content w-full p-6 flex flex-col gap-6">
      <!-- Card principal -->
      <div class="glass rounded-box w-full p-8">
        <div class="breadcrumbs text-sm">
          <ul>
            <li><a href="/"><i class="bi bi-house-fill"></i>Inicio</a></li>
            <li>Extra</li>
            <li>Referencias</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <h1 class="mb-5 text-5xl font-bold">Referencias</h1>
        <p>
          Aquí encontrarás una recopilación de fuentes y guías utilizadas para la elaboración de las secciones de
          tecnologías gráficas y configuraciones de videojuegos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Lista de referencias -->
      <div class="glass rounded-box w-full p-6">
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-left space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li>
            Hardwarepulse, Anti-Aliasing. (12 de Marzo de 2018).
            <a
              href="https://www.hardwarepulse.com/2018/03/12/para-que-sirve-el-anti-aliasing/"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">https://www.hardwarepulse.com/2018/03/12/para-que-sirve-el-anti-aliasing/</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Madboxpc, ¿Qué significa cada opción? (1 de junio de 2013).
            <a
              href="https://www.madboxpc.com/guia-graficos-en-videojuegos-que-significa-cada-opcion/"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary"
              >https://www.madboxpc.com/guia-graficos-en-videojuegos-que-significa-cada-opcion/</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Nvidia, The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt. Andrew Burnes (18 de Mayo de 2015).
            <a
              href="https://www.geforce.com/whats-new/guides/the-witcher-3-wild-hunt-graphics-performance-and-tweaking-guide#the-witcher-3-wild-hunt-pc-exclusive-graphics-enhancements"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">Guía de The Witcher 3</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Wikipedia, Nvidia GameWorks. (31 de Octubre de 2017).
            <a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nvidia_GameWorks" target="_blank" class="link link-primary"
              >https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nvidia_GameWorks</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Wikipedia, PhysX. (21 de Febrero de 2019).
            <a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/PhysX" target="_blank" class="link link-primary"
              >https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/PhysX</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Nvidia, Rise of the Tomb Raider Guide. Andrew Burnes (28 de Enero de 2016).
            <a
              href="https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/geforce/guides/rise-of-the-tomb-raider-graphics-and-performance-guide/"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">Guía de Rise of the Tomb Raider</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Nvidia, Control Guide. Andrew Burnes (27 de Agosto de 2019).
            <a
              href="https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/geforce/guides/control-graphics-and-performance-guide/"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">Guía de Control</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Nvidia, Destiny 2 Guide. Andrew Burnes (17 de Octubre de 2017).
            <a
              href="https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/geforce/news/destiny-2-pc-graphics-and-performance-guide/"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">Guía de Destiny 2</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            PCGamingWiki, Depth of Field Comparison.
            <a
              href="https://community.pcgamingwiki.com/gallery/image/949-comparison-depth-of-field-high/"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">Comparación Depth of Field</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            VC-JCSS, SSDO.
            <a
              href="https://vc-jcss.github.io/vc/docs/workshops/rendering/globalIllumination/SSDO"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">https://vc-jcss.github.io/vc/docs/workshops/rendering/globalIllumination/SSDO</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Epic Games, Planar Reflections.
            <a
              href="https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/planar-reflections-in-unreal-engine"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">Planar Reflections en Unreal Engine</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Epic Games, Anti-Aliasing and Upscaling.
            <a
              href="https://dev.epicgames.com/documentation/en-us/unreal-engine/anti-aliasing-and-upscaling-in-unreal-engine"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">Anti-Aliasing en Unreal Engine</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Unity Docs, Cubemap.
            <a
              href="https://docs.unity3d.com/es/2020.2/Manual/class-Cubemap.html"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">https://docs.unity3d.com/es/2020.2/Manual/class-Cubemap.html</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            Tipos de Ventiladores PC.
            <a
              href="https://www.opirata.com/blog/tipos-de-ventiladores-pc-guia-completa/"
              target="_blank"
              class="link link-primary">https://www.opirata.com/blog/tipos-de-ventiladores-pc-guia-completa/</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DashboardLayout>
